{"tid":1700022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人必需要承認一個事實: 呢個政權已經將所有現有抗爭既道路封死, 唔搵新出路, 場運動只有枯萎一個可能","createTime":"2019-11-08T09:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:37:57.000Z","uid":196536,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d72c0e138bc0560094b382c474db9a0be890c87","tid":1700022,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"集會: 有不反又點?叫你腰斬再趕你走; 冇不反? 直接拉曬你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行: 唔批不反, 再圍捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆: 食環日日清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐黃店: 搵狗查ID<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信抗爭去到今日民意已經牢固, 但十個抗爭者不論和勇, 而家都可能有個問題就係我有咩可以做?<br />\n今日既中午快閃中環係一個啟發, 之前有巴打提議既輪班制, 亦都係一個可行既建議.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1694676/page/4\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1694676/page/4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=411300c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ</a><br />\n簡單黎講, 即係和理非&quot;軍團&quot;化. <br />\n除左呢樣, 我諗仲有好多野可以做. 希望手足從此要諗多步行多步, 我地每做多一步, 就可以救多個後生仔.<br />\n香港已經係世界抗爭既先驅, 而我地, 就係香港既先驅!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">手足血仇 此生必報</span></span>"},{"pid":"94ea7a3ea99c3b028d21396576b4404b0ae24c09","tid":1700022,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"集思"},{"pid":"233fbca139c9cb9269756a1a701e906d824af89f","tid":1700022,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"你肯定民意穩固？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxeN9ge.jpg&h=69dfcf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93d3sB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93d3sB8.jpg&h=cb63a975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足只係condom，議席最重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5a4eaa877999401ae9eaf1fb8c1376ea850e93","tid":1700022,"uid":196536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"233fbca139c9cb9269756a1a701e906d824af89f","tid":1700022,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"你肯定民意穩固？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxeN9ge.jpg&h=69dfcf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93d3sB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93d3sB8.jpg&h=cb63a975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足只係condom，議席最重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，貼撚完未呀"},{"pid":"442313564bc12c7574f8eed43c227f6cc3f3a481","tid":1700022,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8611b950942a5a8250685ad54d766d27194acee1","tid":1700022,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"推，一定要堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n用任何方法都好"},{"pid":"f2d77173498231df110340f34409e40e4ac10b33","tid":1700022,"uid":30988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"233fbca139c9cb9269756a1a701e906d824af89f","tid":1700022,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"你肯定民意穩固？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http